类 Range.Bound<T extends Comparable<T>>

    Range<T extends Comparable<T>>

    public static class Range.Bound<T extends Comparable<T>>
extends Object
    Value object representing a boundary. A boundary can either be unbounded, including its value or its value.
    从以下版本开始:
    2.0
